subsection.content:
In any matter referred to it under this article, the Committee may call upon
                the States Parties concerned, referred to in subparagraph (b), to supply any
                relevant information;

The States Parties concerned, referred to in subparagraph (b), shall have the
                right to be represented when the matter is being considered by the Committee and to
                make submissions orally and/or in writing;

If a solution within the terms of subparagraph (e) is reached, the Committee
                shall confine its report to a brief statement of the facts and of the solution
                reached;
